public class TextStyleImpl extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl implements TextStyle
An implementation of the model object 'Text Style'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Underline
  • Underline Style
  • Strikeout
  • Font
  • Foreground
  • Background
  • Underline Color
  • Strikeout Color
